00:15:33,845 --> 00:15:36,011
{\an1}<i>There's no way out of this</i>
<i>waterfall area.</i>

217
00:15:36,676 --> 00:15:40,009
{\an1}<i>What?! So we just have to wait</i>
<i>'til someone comes to rescue</i>
<i>us?! </i>

