234
00:16:35,811 --> 00:16:39,308
{\an1}<i>Your team and ours will start</i>
<i>out close to each other for the</i>
<i>Second Exam.</i>

235
00:16:39,976 --> 00:16:45,205
{\an1}<i>However, a Hidden Leaf team with</i>
<i>a Byakugan user will also be</i>
<i>nearby. They're quite strong. </i>

