00:16:54,133 --> 00:16:58,631
{\an1}<i>Their team is not to be take</i>
<i>lightly. But still,...we'll slow</i>
<i>them down.</i>

239
00:16:59,631 --> 00:17:03,128
{\an1}<i>While we do,...I want you to get</i>
<i>as far away from them as</i>
<i>possible. </i>

240
00:17:04,161 --> 00:17:05,028
Oh...?

241
00:17:06,260 --> 00:17:09,092
{\an1}In other words, you're gonna
order us all around, is that it?

242
00:17:09,592 --> 00:17:12,958
{\an1}I merely want as many Sand as
