00:17:51,202 --> 00:17:51,869
<i>Hey!</i>

256
00:17:52,936 --> 00:17:54,467
{\an1}<i>You're just too good with that</i>
<i>fan...</i>

257
00:17:55,199 --> 00:17:57,966
