00:18:02,796 --> 00:18:03,362
<i>Squirmy...</i>

261
00:18:03,596 --> 00:18:06,028
<i>little--! </i>

262
00:18:10,692 --> 00:18:15,024
{\an1}<i>I learned from Shira, too! I can</i>
<i>use this Evasion Jutsu better</i>
<i>than anyone! </i>

263
00:18:16,188 --> 00:18:19,186
{\an1}<i>I know your moves...like the</i>
